        <mxCell id="KBxd40oUGaLzeB0K-hSW-17" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;## Tópicos (Kafka)&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- tucc-sync-event&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;- tucc-sync-event.dlq&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;- tucc-sync-event.retry&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="170" width="340" x="487" y="1720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="KBxd40oUGaLzeB0K-hSW-40" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;# Sobre os projetos&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;## tucc-sync-db-producer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Projeto que escuta as modificações do banco de dados Oracle (legado) através do Debezium, ele usa o conector do Kafka, mapeia os dados e publica uma mensagem em um tópico. A mensagem contém dados referente a uma tabela específica do Oracle, isso servirá de orientação no consumir para a sincronização dos dados.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;## tucc-sync-db-consumer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Projeto que consome as mensagens do tópico do Kafka para inserir os dados no banco de dados Postgres, realizando um mapeamento dos dados, identificando qual tabela teve a modificação e qual foi o tipo da alteração (UPDATE, DELETE), por fim realizando a sincronização dos dados.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;## tucc-core&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Projeto que disponibiliza endpoints para consumo dos gateways ou clients, aqui tem conexão com o Postgres para listar itens do banco de dados Postgres. Não há alterações de dados nesse banco, apenas leitura, já que os dados são inseridos no Oracle através de um legado.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;##&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;tucc-monolito&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Projeto legado desenvolvido em Java 8, JSP, Struts, Javascript, Ajax e Oracle. Através dele é alimentada a base de dados que será útil para a sincronização, ou migração, dos dados para o Postgres na arquitetura de microsserviços.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="440" width="1110" x="40" y="710" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="KBxd40oUGaLzeB0K-hSW-41" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;## Tecnologias (microsserviços)&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Java 21&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Spring Boot&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Spring JPA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Apache Kafka&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Postgres&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Oracle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;- Debezium&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="410" x="40" y="1720" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
